title: What are you seeing as your Prs value?
content:
What are you seeing as your Prs value? (which displays after enabling Developer options and selecting "Pointer Location".

On my 3aXL I have problems glide typing and scrolling. Input will cut in and out. My Prs is stuck at 1.0. And red. Is this normal?
My Nexus 5x varies this value.
Please help. Thank you
